<h2>Permit Information</h2>
<a href='http://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/weightedlottery.htm'>http://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/weightedlottery.htm</a>
<p>
Permits for the Grand Canyon are required and available through a weighted lottery system in February (additional dates may be distributed throughout the year). </p>
